tern Cooperative Oncology Group study. $J Clin Oncol. 1995;13(6):1430-1435.$<br> Kirschling RJ, Grill JP, Marks RS, et al. Paclitaxel and G-CSF in previously untreated patients with extensive-stage small-cell lung cancer: a phase II study of the North Central Cancer Treatment Group. $Am J Clin Oncol. 1999;22(5):517-522$<br>', null, '<b>Paclitaxel</b> 250 mg/m<sup>2</sup> IV over 24 hours<br> Repeat every 21 days', null);
