	<li>Cisplatin (Platinol)&nbsp;70 mg/m<sup>2</sup>&nbsp;IV in 1 liter normal saline once on day 2
	<ul>
		<li>Split dose could be used at physician discretion for patients with CrCl less than 60 mL/min/1.73m<sup>2</sup>: 35 mg/m<sup>2</sup>&nbsp;IV once per day on days 1 &amp; 2</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
</ul>

<h4>Supportive medications</h4>

<ul>
