<p><strong><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">Renal Impairment:</span></strong></p>

<p><em><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">Prior to treatment initiation:</span></em><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"> No dosage adjustment necessary. </span></p>

<p><em><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">During treatment:</span></em></p>

<ul>
	<li><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">Grade 2: Withhold pembrolizumab; administer corticosteroids (prednisone 1-2 mg/kg/day [or equivalent] followed by a taper); may resume upon recovery to grade 0 or 1 toxicity.</span></li>
	<li><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">Grade 3 or 4: Permanently discontinue pembrolizumab; administer corticosteroids (prednisone 1-2 mg/kg/day [or equivalent] followed by a taper).</span></li>
